<br>
- Mez summoned creature<br>
- Charm summoned creature (not random duration, fixed.)<br>
- Summon Fishing Pole (Only item in the game that breaks, may as well be able to make a new one.)<br>
- Summon Bane weapon.  (Target a mob and cast the spell, summons a weapon with mostly bane damage towards that type of monster.  Doesn't work for Seru and Emp of course.)<br>
- Limit and Give us back that preposed anti summon spell<br>
- Summon Robe (Come on, I can make a full suit of armor for my buddy but I can't even make a robe for myself?)<br>
- Fiery Bolt of Whatever (Bolt doing 1600 damage at 60th level.)<br>
- Elemental Guardian (Summon a lesser elemental to protect another character like an enchanters pet would protect him.  You have to remain in zone, and character has to agree to accept pet.)<br>
- Group Call of the Hero.<br>
- Summon Fast Food (When *FAST* just isn't quick enough..)<br>
- Summon poison (weak type for rogues)<br>
- Change Expulse summons to lure based spells and increase damage by 10%<br>
- Reduce casting time on decoy<br>
- Summon Compass (Help out the newbs)<br>
- Creeping Malosi (Continues to debuff a few points every tick from monster, when it wears off monster is no longer debuffed.  Potential to debuff more than normal malosi.)<br>
<br>
Heck I'll throw in some AA ability ideas too..<br>
- Improved Pet heal (Pet healing spells heal 10, 25 then 50% more.)<br>
- Certain Pet (All pets are summoned at the max level first time through.)<br>
- Spellcasting Aptitude (Minimum damage a spell can do if partially resisted is 10%,25%,or 50% depending on level of skill.)<br>
- Elemental Link (Pet doesn't die when HP depleated, damage suffered by pet is suffered by caster too.  Caster only starts suffering damage after pet HP depleted.)<br>
- Elemental Mastery Earth, Air, Fire, Water. (Each separate skill.  When affected by each the caster always summons pets as if he were holding a staff of elemental mastery.)<br>
- Bolt Mastery (Casting time for bolt spells is reduced by 5,10,15%  On top of what is given from casting alacrity.)<br>
<br>
I think most of these are reasonable ideas.. Well ok, maybe not the fast food one.  Can't blame me for trying though. =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uusrbinperldashw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>usrbinperl dashw</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 84<br> <font color=#333333>(7/20/02 10:23:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1391.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Some more ideas</span><hr size=1> Hmm, some good ideas there from Sirellyn...<br>
