<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> - Change Expulse summons to lure based spells and increase damage by 10%<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Totally agree.  It's complete BS that a spell with such limited application is so worthless.  I don't even use it in The Hole, Char is much better.  WTF bother to give us such spells if there's no advantage to them?  Lure and increased damage (possibly with increased mana as well) would make these actually worth using in those ever so rare situations where you fight summoned beings.<br>
